Comment: 1,0:02:04.40,0:02:09.82,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,只為改變這世間
Comment: 1,0:02:12.51,0:02:15.18,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,Fighting Gold
Comment: 1,0:02:15.24,0:02:24.95,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,唯有相信自己的內心之人 終有一天方能閃耀
Comment: 1,0:02:25.59,0:02:33.84,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,燃燒全部生命 即便是神亦無畏懼 戰鬥永不停息
Comment: 1,0:02:34.08,0:02:38.56,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,不屈的魂靈
Comment: 1,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.98,JOJO5-op1-ch,,0,0,0,karaoke,Fighting Gold
